<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Proposal Sent</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9fafb; }
        .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸ“‹ New Proposal Sent</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello {{recipientName}},</h2>
            <p>A new proposal has been sent to you:</p>
            
            <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3>{{proposalTitle}}</h3>
                <p><strong>From:</strong> {{senderName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{sentDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Please review the proposal and take the necessary action.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{proposalLink}}" class="button">View Proposal</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact the sender directly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent by the Proposal Management System</p>
            <p>Â© 2024 Proposal Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
